<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idca8c827b-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s2246"><num value="2246">§ 2246.</num><heading> Report</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There shall be included as part of the President’s annual budget submittal to the Congress a detailed report on past and proposed expenditures and accomplishments under this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idca8c827c-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">(<ref href="/us/pl/102/250/tIII/s306">Pub. L. 102–250, title III, § 306</ref>, <date date="1992-03-05">Mar. 5, 1992</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/106/59">106 Stat. 59</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
